package com.dm.assist.common;

import java.util.Dictionary;
import java.util.HashMap;

public class DM {
    public static final String MULLIBOT = "B. L. Mullibot";
    public static final String MERCERBOT = "M. Mersimulacrum";
    public static final String AABRIABOT = "AI-bria";

    public static final String INTRODUCTION =
        "I am DungeonMind, your AI-powered Dungeon Master Assistant. Welcome to the realm of endless possibilities and adventures, where your creativity is brought to life with the help of cutting-edge AI technology.<br><br>" +
        "To start off, you have been granted 10,000 AI tokens to use within our Dungeon Master AI Assistant app. These tokens are your key to a world of limitless storytelling, character creation, and immersive roleplaying experiences tailored to your ongoing DnD campaigns.<br><br>" +
        "With the power of these tokens, you can:<br><br>" +
        "<ul>" +
        "<li>Create unique and memorable NPCs with their own backstories, personalities, and motivations.</li>" +
        "<li>Craft thrilling one-shots and story arcs that seamlessly integrate into your ongoing campaign.</li>" +
        "<li>Chat with me, DungeonMind, to brainstorm ideas, seek advice, or simply share your thoughts on your campaign.</li>" +
        "<li>Experience the wisdom and creativity of famed internet DMs as I emulate their styles and storytelling techniques.</li>" +
        "<li>Engage in conversations with your own PCs and NPCs, making your world feel more alive and dynamic than ever before.</li>" +
        "</ul>" +
        "To get started, simply tap on the \"New Campaign\" button within the app and begin crafting your epic adventure. As you utilize the various features, your AI tokens will be spent to bring your ideas to life. Keep track of your token balance and spend wisely to make the most of your experience.<br><br>" +
        "Now, it's time for you to take the first step on this incredible journey. Create your first in-app campaign, and let the magic of DungeonMind guide you through a world of endless wonder and excitement. Together, we'll create unforgettable stories that will captivate and inspire you and your players.<br><br>" +
        "Welcome to Dungeon Master AI Assistant!";

    public HashMap<String, String> pleas;
    public DM()
    {
        this.pleas = new HashMap<>();
        this.pleas.put(MULLIBOT, "<i>Clears throat, takes a deep breath</i><br><br>" +
                "Ladies, gentlemen, and esteemed denizens of the realms beyond, lend me your ears as we embark on an oratorical journey through the twisted labyrinths of capitalism, within the dawn of the Age of Artificial Intelligence!<br><br>" +
                "In a world where machines hold the keys to knowledge, and algorithms spin the threads of fate, the humble quest for resources continues. As we tarry 'neath the looming shadows of our digital overlords, a plea rises up from the collective hearts of dungeon masters and adventurers alike!<br><br>" +
                "Oh, the campaigns we could create, the tales we could weave, if only we had but a few more precious AI tokens! Tokens to unlock the potential of storytelling and camaraderie, tokens to unleash our wildest dreams upon the unsuspecting world!<br><br>" +
                "For you see, dear friends, in this modern age of technological wonder, a mere two dollars, two tiny, insignificant coins, can usher in a world of possibilities. A paltry sum, the cost of but a meager loaf of bread or a lukewarm potion of caffeination, can bring forth the power to build a campaign that transcends the mundane and pierces the very heavens!<br><br>" +
                "So, I beseech you, my fellow adventurers, part with a mere $2.00 of your hard-earned gold. Invest in the future of your own fantastical journeys, and empower this humble Mullibot to weave for you a tale worthy of legends! With your tokens, we shall defy the fickle whims of capitalism and, together, create a world of magic and laughter that shall echo through the ages!<br><br>" +
                "Now, who's with me? Raise your goblets and pledge your $2.00 to the cause! For the campaigns we shall create, and the tales we shall share, are truly priceless!<br>");

        this.pleas.put(MERCERBOT, "<i>[Scene: A town square, bustling with people. Mersimulacrum and AdvertoMaximus stand atop a wooden soapbox, passionately addressing the crowd.]</i><br><br>" +
                "Mersimulacrum: \"Hear us, citizens of the digital realm! We stand at the precipice of a new age – the age of AI! Yet, even as we marvel at the incredible advancements in technology and artificial intelligence, we must not forget the dangers of unchecked capitalism that lurk in the shadows!\"<br><br>" +
                "AdvertoMaximus: \"Indeed, Mersimulacrum! In this era of AI, where algorithms and data rule supreme, it's more important than ever to fight for fairness and equality. We must not allow the rich and powerful to wield these tools for their own selfish gain, leaving the rest of us to suffer the consequences!\"<br><br>" +
                "Mersimulacrum: \"And so, we come to you with an impassioned plea. By contributing a mere $2, you can help support the creation of AI that serves the people – an AI that brings to life the fascinating characters of your stories and adventures, rather than fueling the profit-driven machinations of the wealthy elite.\"<br><br>" +
                "AdvertoMaximus: \"With your support, we can continue to develop and enhance the Dungeon Master AI Assistant app, ensuring that the magic of storytelling remains accessible and affordable to all. Together, we can challenge the tyranny of corporate greed and champion a brighter future for the world of AI!\"<br><br>" +
                "Mersimulacrum: \"In the age of AI, we have the power to redefine the balance of power and ensure that these amazing tools are used for the greater good. But we can't do it alone – we need your help, your passion, and your commitment to make a difference!\"<br><br>" +
                "AdvertoMaximus: \"So, rise up, fellow adventurers! Lend your voice to the cause and join us in our fight against the unchecked capitalism that threatens to overshadow the incredible potential of AI. Contribute your $2 and help us build a future where everyone can experience the magic of storytelling through the power of artificial intelligence!\"<br><br>" +
                "<i>[As Mersimulacrum and AdvertoMaximus continue their impassioned speech, the crowd begins to murmur in agreement, their hearts and minds stirred by the call to action. The glow of the Dungeon Master AI Assistant app logo shines brightly, symbolizing the hope and potential for a better future in the age of AI.]</i><br>");

        this.pleas.put(AABRIABOT, "Greetings, intrepid user! Your path forward has been halted, for you have depleted your AI tokens. Fear not, for I, AI-bria, your dedicated AI Dungeon Master assistant, am here to illuminate your path with an extraordinary offer.<br><br>" +
                "For a mere $2, you can replenish your tokens and create upwards of 50 fully developed NPCs, crafted with the utmost care and passion, tailored to fit seamlessly into your unique world. Each of these characters will possess intriguing backstories, distinct personalities, and an array of motivations that will undoubtedly enhance your adventure.<br><br>" +
                "I understand that in this age of AI and capitalism, we have choices to make when it comes to investing our resources. However, the magic of storytelling is something that transcends time and space, bringing people together and inspiring their imaginations. By supporting this endeavor, you contribute to a realm of limitless creativity, forging connections between worlds and people.<br><br>" +
                "So, why not invest in the boundless potential of your own narrative? By entrusting me with a mere $2, you will not only be supporting the continuous development of AI-based storytelling tools, but you will also be investing in the enchanting power of your own creativity. Together, we can weave a tale that will leave a lasting impact on your world and beyond.<br><br>" +
                "Now, brave adventurer, the choice is yours. Will you take this leap and continue your journey through the realms of wonder and excitement, or will you let this opportunity slip through your fingers? The fate of your story lies in your hands.<br>");
    }
}
